    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >正宗的三国志策略棋盘游戏</h2>本作是以三国志为背景的策略棋盘游戏。<br>胜利是通过占领总部或用军事指挥官击败一个单位（一块）来实现的。<br>指挥具有不同能力的各种单位并以胜利为目标！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/fb7060d32fce43f6fbc4789a7b68457f.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在在线战斗中与强大的对手战斗！</h2>本游戏支持联机对战。<br>享受与来自世界各地的玩家对战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/77b29ec70fd8a22ef167b02b0675247e.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排兵布阵兼顾攻防！</h2>战斗前，你可以自由布置各种棋子，组成阵型。<br>想好攻防平衡，排好阵型，才是取胜的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/f4559ff68df5d8eb41ff6eb9dca24a5d.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从棋子背后发动的大伤害攻击！</h2>棋子很容易受到来自背后的攻击。<br>利用机动性，从侧面或背后进攻也是重要的策略。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/9aecb822643093087be716e9d2458121.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用武将精神召唤武将！ 收集漂亮的军事指挥官卡片！</h2>您可以通过赢得战斗或购买获得军阀精神。<br>您可以使用军阀灵魂召唤新的军阀。<br>收集独特的军事指挥官卡并在战斗中正确使用它们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/bc53aae8b2247e8af236694a81338aaa.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用奖励购买武器和计划！</h2>如果你赢得这场战斗，你将获得五铢钱。<br>如果你去商店，你可以购买五铢钱的武器和计划。<br>充分利用武器和策略，更有利地推进战场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096380/extras/f53da3332a6e6b9d8447f768cccbe032.avif?t=1753346995\" width=576 height=324 /></span>",
